quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  21,29,"Kala e ma…ď…ďe kadi wi'u…óo: \"Min ko mi rewetee…óo gaanin Makko\". On …óon Men Yo…ďay mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Men Yo…ďirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  21,30,"Enee, hara …ďen yeddu…ďe yi'aali wonndema kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin …ói laatinoke hippondir…ói, Men Udditi …ói Men wa…ói immorde e ndiyam …óam kala huunde wuuru nde. Kaa …ďe gom…óintaa"
  21,31,"Men wa…ói ka leydi pelle fii wata nde oo√Īodo e ma…ď…ďe, Men wa…ói e mayri …óate yaaju…óe, belajo'o kam…ďe …ďe feeway"
  21,32,"Men wa…ói kammu ngun kippudi reenaandi, kam…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe gaayi Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  21,33,Ko Kanko woni On Tagu…óo jemma on e √Īalorma on e naange ngen e lewru ndun kala majji hi…ói fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku
  21,34,"Men wa…óanaali …ďanndunke ado maa…óa luttineede, enee, hara si a maayii ko kam…ďe woni luttintee…ďe …ďen"
  21,35,"Kala wonkii meedat may…óe nden, Men jarribora on bone on e mo∆ī∆īere nden jarrabagol, ko ka Amen kadi ruttoto…óon"
  21,36,"Si …ďen yeddu…ďe yi'ii ma, …ďe jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde […ďe wi‚Äôa:] \"Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaŇčtotoo…óo rewetee…ói mo'on …óin?\" hara kam…ďe ko …ďe yeddu…ďe jantagol Hinnorante On"
  21,37,"Ne…ó…óake on Tagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am …óen wata on hawju"
  21,38,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  21,39,"Sinndo …ďen yeddu…ďe anndiino tuma tawi …ďe ittataa Yiite ngen ka geece ma…ď…ďe wanaa kadi ka …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe kadi, kam…ďe …ďe wonaali walloytee…ďe"
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee nge muga …ďe, hara …ďe hattantaake ruttugol nge, …ďe wonaali kadi nennanoytee…ďe"
  21,41,"Gom…óii Nulaa…ďe goo jalkitanooma ado maa…óa, jippii e …ďen jalkitu…ďe ko …ďe laatinoo hi…ďe jalkita"
  21,42,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e √Īalorma immorde e Hinnorante On, ko woni, kam…ďe gaayi jaŇčta Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe"
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani …ďe reewetee…ďe …ďe no dannda …ďe gaanin Amen? ∆Āe hattantaake wallude hay wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe, wanaa kam…ďe woni wondatee…ďe immorde e Amen"
  21,44,"Ko woni, Men dakmitii …ďee e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen haa ngurndam …óam juutani …ďe. Enee, hara …ďee yi'aali wonnde Menen Me…óen ara e leydi ndin Men ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kam…ďe woni fooloo…ďe …ďen"
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si …ďe jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii …ďe see…óa immorde e Lepte Joomi maa …óen, maa …ďe wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke too√Īu…ďe"
  21,47,"Men wa…óa manndikir…óe(peesir…óe) Nun…óal ngal fii √Ďalnde Darngal hara wonkii woo to√Īiroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii Hasboo…ďe"
  21,48,Gom…óii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaŇčta wonannde huloo…ďe …ďen
  21,49,∆Āen hulay…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka wirnii hara kam…ďe immorde e Darngal ngal ko …ďe huli
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] ko nde JaŇčta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yedday…ďe nde"